.list-group
  - timers.each do |timer|
    %a.list-group-item{href: '#', onclick: "toggleCheckbox($(this)); return false;", data: {activeclass: "list-group-item-info"}}
      .row
        .col-xs-6.col-md-2
          = I18n.l timer.date
        .col-xs-6.col-md-7
          %strong
            = timer.task.name
        .col-xs-6.col-md-2.text-right
          %span.label.label-primary
            = number_to_currency timer.value, unit: "h"
        .col-xs-6.col-md-1
          .checkbox.pull-right
            = check_box_tag "timer_ids[]", {name: timer.task.name, task_uuid: timer.task_id, uuid: timer.id, value: timer.value.to_f}.to_json, false, id: dom_id(timer)
            %label{for: dom_id(timer)}

  - if timers.blank?
